games.spiders

Class Nest

  • java.lang.Object
    • joueur.BaseGameObject
      • games.spiders.GameObject
        • games.spiders.Nest

  • public class Nest
extends GameObject
    A location (node) connected to other Nests via Webs (edges) in the game that Spiders can converge on, regardless of owner.
